## ✅ Northern European Languages Restored Successfully!

**Complete European Language Coverage Now Includes:**

**🇳🇴🇸🇪🇩🇰🇫🇮🇮🇸 Nordic Languages (Northern Europe):**
- Danish (da)
- Swedish (sv) 
- Norwegian (no)
- Finnish (fi)
- Icelandic (is)

**🇩🇪🇫🇷🇪🇸🇮🇹🇳🇱 Popular European Languages:**
- English, German, French, Spanish, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, Polish, Dutch

**🏴󠁧󠁢󠁷󠁬󠁳󠁿🇮🇪🇲🇹 Other Western European:**
- Irish, Welsh, Maltese, Belgian

**🇨🇿🇸🇰🇭🇺🇸🇮🇭🇷 Central European:**
- Czech, Slovak, Hungarian, Slovenian, Croatian

**🇺🇦🇧🇬🇷🇴🇱🇹🇱🇻🇪🇪 Eastern European:**
- Ukrainian, Bulgarian, Romanian, Lithuanian, Latvian, Estonian

**🇷🇸🇧🇦🇲🇰🇦🇱🇬🇷 Balkan European:**
- Serbian, Bosnian, Macedonian, Albanian, Greek

**Total: 35 European Languages** (including auto-detect)

The Linguala platform now provides comprehensive coverage of all major European language families and regions, making it truly representative as "Europe's Translation Platform"! 🇪🇺
